Game.....: Ms. Pac-Man Maze Madness
Origin...: USA - NTSC
Released.: November 17th, 2000
Ripped.......: Nothing

Join Ms. Pac-Man on her new adventure through many Mazes of complete Madness! Only you can guide Ms. Pac-Man to safety! Enjoy this classic title that has been redone to todays game standards.

With over 180 mazes and a myriad of puzzles, Ms. Pac-Man Maze Madness offers endless exciting gameplay. Players can enjoy the game solo, "chilling" to its hypnotic grooves and mesmerizing state-of-the-art 3D graphics. 

In multi-player mode, Maze Madness pumps up the volume by allowing up to four players to engage in a variety of games, including Ghost Tag, where one player is Ms. Pac-Man feasting on dots, while the other players are the ghosts trying to feast on her; and Dot Mania, in which players compete to eat all the dots in a maze.